interpretation: The avocado card represents abundance and nourishment. Like the creamy fruit inside, this card brings an inner richness that can sustain you through difficult times. The avocado reminds you to take care of yourself and prioritize self-care, while also being generous and giving to those around you. This card can signify a time of growth and fertility, as well as a reminder to honor the cycles of nature and your own body. Embrace the richness of life and enjoy the fruits of your labor.
